review 1: Great atmosphere, good food with reasonable price
review 2: Restaurant with fishing pond with gazebo around the pool. Many varian menu with affordable price and suitable for event gathering and birthday party. also suitable for family with children enjoy week end. This place is romantic for couple.
review 3:
Nice place with good ambience.
They have good food but the fried rice was so so.
They have specious gazebos and live music in the evening.
Reasonable price.
The only challenge is the road is really bad.
review 4: Delicious food, cosy place. Serve halal food with affordable price. They praying are for moslems, and it's also clean. There are playing ground for kids, and you can also spend time fishing.
review 5: A nice open air restaurant with lake and good food - best is ikan bakar and other fish dishes. The place is difficult to find.
